div.h3: About “List of Game of Thrones Deaths”

div.p: This is an annotated list of every major character death in HBO’s Game of Thrones. If there’s a character you feel we missed, feel free to add him or her to the list. Try to include GIFs, YouTube links, or pictures that correspond with the deaths.

p.a: Mourn them here if you want.
